@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
title UTXO transaction flow (shared by Bitcoin and Cardano)

package "UTXO set (before)" {
  [UTXO_1\n3,000] as U1
  [UTXO_2\n2,000] as U2
  [other UTXOs...] as UX
}

rectangle "Transaction\ninputs = outputs + fee" as TX

package "UTXO set (after)" {
  [To Bob\n4,500 (new)] as O1
  [Change to Alice\n300 (new)] as O2
  [other UTXOs...] as UX2
}

U1 --> TX : consumed
U2 --> TX : consumed
TX --> O1 : created
TX --> O2 : created
UX -[hidden]-> UX2

note bottom of TX
  Consumed UTXOs leave the set permanently;
  each is spendable exactly once. New outputs
  become available for future transactions.
end note
@enduml
